      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like there's no real reason to keep pushing through it. if everything is just a loop of suffering and eventual nothingness, then why is the default expectation that we have to keep going? wouldn't it be more logical to just... stop? to just opt out when you realize the game is rigged and meaningless?",
